905
00:39:04,460 --> 00:39:05,300
Niuniu.

906
00:39:05,820 --> 00:39:06,660
Niuniu.

907
00:39:06,860 --> 00:39:07,940
You're Niuniu.

908
00:39:08,980 --> 00:39:10,060
She's not your daughter.

909
00:39:10,080 --> 00:39:11,360
