You look just like her.

918
00:39:25,220 --> 00:39:26,500
When other kids

919
00:39:26,500 --> 00:39:27,660
went out to play,

920
00:39:28,020 --> 00:39:29,460
she never joined them.

921
00:39:30,020 --> 00:39:32,420
She was always making tofu with me.

922
00:39:32,900 --> 00:39:34,940
Before she went missing,

923
