926
00:39:41,700 --> 00:39:43,340
Where did she go?

927
00:39:43,860 --> 00:39:44,700
Niuniu.

928
00:39:45,100 --> 00:39:46,580
Niuniu.

929
00:39:48,660 --> 00:39:49,580
Niuniu.

930
00:39:51,500 --> 00:39:52,900
Where are you, Niuniu?

931
00:39:52,900 --> 00:39:53,740
I'm not her.

932
00:39:56,020 --> 00:39:57,340
Niuniu.

933
00:39:57,980 --> 00:39:59,540
Have you seen a child like this?

934
00:39:59,540 --> 00:40:00,380
No.

935
00:40:06,060 --> 00:40:07,580
Marquis Changxing's Mansion.

936
00:40:10,300 --> 00:40:12,380
Aman, get me paper and an envelope.

937
00:40:12,780 --> 00:40:13,620
Yes.

938
00:40:18,300 --> 00:40:20,300
